				<div class="entry-meta">
			<span class="byline"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://localhost/onething/author/u843867/">Justin Jones</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><a href="http://localhost/onething/2013/01/11/markup-html-tags-and-formatting/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2013-01-11T20:22:19+00:00">11th January 2013</time><time class="updated" datetime="2015-10-08T08:37:57+00:00">8th October 2015</time></a></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
